{{Use Indian English|date=April 2018}}
'''Zindagi Live Foundation''' is a [[NGO]] based in [[Ludhiana]], [[India]] which works for children affected with [[Thalassemia]] by giving them financial help and organizing blood donation camps.<ref>{{cite news|title=Zindagi Live dedicated to save lives|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/ludhiana/community/zindagi-live-dedicated-to-save-lives/37000.html|accessdate=11 July 2015|publisher=''Tribune India''|date=2 February 201}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Zindgi Live Foundation launches free treatment for Hepatitis-C|url=http://www.theindiapost.com/nation/punjab/zindagi-live-foundation-launch-free-treatment-of-hepatitis-c-at-dmc/|accessdate=11 July 2015|publisher=''The India Post''|date=18 December 2011}}</ref>
